{"tid":2253411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"名創優品巴黎首家門店開業","createTime":"2020-10-22T06:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T09:22:14.000Z","uid":118346,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4996c012cd9dbf84ebd933a0b4f23599efa3a9e1","tid":2253411,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"當地時間10月20日，名創優品巴黎首家門店開業，這是該公司自紐交所上市以來在歐洲開設的第一家門店。據悉，名創優品的新店位於巴黎的la chaussie -d' antin 58號，店內80%以上商品價格在10歐元以下。名創優品計劃今年在法國再開兩家門店，在2021年再多開幾家門店。<br />\n<br />\n（智通財經）"},{"pid":"12b4cf802aabcd27e7e70563aaa6bed885b91a53","tid":2253411,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:38:27.000Z","msg":"名創優品首日美國掛牌 收市升4.4%<br />\n<br />\n內地休閒雜貨品牌名創優品(MINISO)在美國首日掛牌買賣，收市價較招股價高4.4%。<br />\n<br />\n名創優品周四收市報20.88美元，市值相當於63.5億美元。<br />\n<br />\n該公司以每股20美元出售3040萬份ADS，集資6.08億美元(47.4億港元)。名創優品的股東包括騰訊(00700)。"},{"pid":"48a77ceedb060eae704c30c93bc2c1bbfb07f640","tid":2253411,"uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"Flying tiger好佢幾條街"},{"pid":"fbd98c8b21c017f9a94fbfe06cbab174f62084f4","tid":2253411,"uid":362121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:55:06.000Z","msg":"鬼佬自己攞嚟，養大左中國 依家比中國反攻"},{"pid":"166170bf778fec8e35e19d03f9adcff119e9dd2d","tid":2253411,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"賣大陸野果間？"},{"pid":"c53c4531e9fb2cb92e94ebafcde80a15e17a828a","tid":2253411,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"166170bf778fec8e35e19d03f9adcff119e9dd2d","tid":2253411,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"賣大陸野果間？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"3e7e6cff3bce64948c74daeafecd3faaf21e371f","tid":2253411,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"淘寶曲線進攻歐洲<img src=\"/asset